Name: Caf√© de Poort
Review Text: Kinda shabby but not in a bad way. We were looking for an escape from the rain; somewhere not too busy but not too quiet and Cafe De Poort turned out to be perfect. Great barman, really friendly, and a nice mix of local life and visitors. Totally relaxed atmosphere. Give this place a try.
